                        <span class="fa fa-arrow-down"></span> Section 4b : QUALITATIVE ASSESSMENT(Core Competence)
                    </h6>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseFive1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive1" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
